fields.question: What is PurelyOrganic?
fields.answer: PurelyOrganic is an online marketplace dedicated to organic and eco-friendly products.

fields.question: How can I contact customer support?
fields.answer: You can contact customer support via the contact form on our website.

fields.question: What payment methods do you accept?
fields.answer: We accept all major credit cards, PayPal, and other secure payment methods.

fields.question: How do I track my order?
fields.answer: You can track your order through your account dashboard on our website. You will also receive email updates with tracking information.

fields.question: What is your return policy?
fields.answer: We offer a 30-day return policy on most products. Items must be returned in their original condition and packaging. Please contact customer support for more details.

fields.question: Are your products certified organic?
fields.answer: Yes, all our products are certified organic by recognized certification bodies.

fields.question: Do you offer international shipping?
fields.answer: Currently, we only ship within Canada. We are working on expanding our shipping options to include international destinations.

fields.question: How can I cancel my order?
fields.answer: To cancel your order, please contact our customer support team as soon as possible. If your order has not yet been processed, we will be able to cancel it for you.

fields.question: Can I change my shipping address after placing an order?
fields.answer: If your order has not yet been shipped, you can change your shipping address by contacting our customer support team.
